## 📊 Quick Reference

| Concept | Pattern | When to Use |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| **Handler** | `async fn handler() -> impl IntoResponse` | Route handler |
| **State** | `axum::Extension<Arc<AppState>>` | Shared state |
| **Extractor** | `Path<(id,)>, Json<Data>, Query<Params>` | Request data |
| **Error** | `Result<T, AppError>` + `IntoResponse` | Error handling |
| **Middleware** | `ServiceBuilder::new().layer(layer)` | Request processing |
| **Layer** | `tower_http::cors::CorsLayer` | CORS, tracing, compression |

