## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# New project
cargo new my-api --name my_api
cd my-api

# Add dependencies
cargo add axum tokio tokio-util
cargo add serde --features derive
cargo add tower --features full
cargo add tower-http --features cors,fs

# Run
cargo run
```

